<div class="hero-unit">
	<h1>VetPALS EDC</h1>
	<h2>VetPALS Electronic Data Capture web platform</h2>

	<div id="homepage_body">
		<div id="homepage_text">
			<h3 class="center"><b>Welcome</b></h3>

			<p>
				Please sign in to continue,
				or make a new account. New account will have to be verified by an admin before they
				become active.
			</p>
			<p>
				If you have any question about this site, or ideas to improve upon the site, 
				email me at <a href="mailto:ian@specri.com">Ian Ellis</a>.
			</p>
